{"tid":690001,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"油站入油時玩唔玩電話?","createTime":"2018-06-04T13:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T16:24:20.000Z","uid":79588,"like":217,"dislike":339,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c0a34fbbcb2f7ac6c6b08024a398d1eff870e1","tid":690001,"uid":79588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"現時在油站禁用電話，只是屬於勸諭性質，並無法例規定，李耀培認為要加強教育及宣傳，讓大眾、特別是駕駛者明白危險性。<br />\n<br />\n他說，使用手機而引發爆炸的機會不足萬分之一，而且香港自從80年代引入無鉛汽油後，油槍設計有改善，汽油亦有蓋蓋住瓶口，防止氣體揮發，他認為香港相當安全。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於有發生爆炸的可能性，故油站仍禁用手機，盧覺強亦指，「為安全著想，最好不要用」。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1454321/女子油站「篤」手機爆炸自焚?mtc=10027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1454321%2F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%B2%B9%E7%AB%99%E3%80%8C%E7%AF%A4%E3%80%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E8%87%AA%E7%84%9A%3Fmtc%3D10027&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=77ac90a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1454321/女子油站「篤」手機爆炸自焚?mtc=10027</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊係玩啦 唔玩隻手晾係到做咩?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔玩 容乜易真係爆炸"},{"pid":"09c3a24b86d08b7a03dd089e153bfe59b2b8a956","tid":690001,"uid":79588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人講下"},{"pid":"4f7b5e3ae8e5f1a7a49b00e59935d5ce67fb019c","tid":690001,"uid":80176,"like":256,"dislike":6,"score":250,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"根據莫非定律<br />\n有機會會爆即係一定會有一次爆<br />\n禁一禁好似好d"},{"pid":"407d370dbd220e8523042363848a4bd9b32a126f","tid":690001,"uid":26112,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"講真就算平時行過聞到陣味都淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會即刻收埋部電話"},{"pid":"0319587252c61f349a864fca41df9d84c16c4b1e","tid":690001,"uid":11374,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"